# ctfatsegment
<b>Install</b>\
\
<i>$ pip install ctfatsegment</i>\
\
<b>Usage (noDB)</b>\
\
Process one patient body fat segmentation:\
\
<i>$ ctfatsegment ct.nii</i>\
\
<b>Usage with DB (unavailable in package)</b>\
\
Process one patient and save to DB\
\
<i>$ python3 segment.py ct.nii</i>
